    "For instance, sodium carbonate monohydrate and sodium carbonate were considered the same reagent.",
    "Furthermore, some reactions in the dataset involved an unusually high number of solvents and reagents.",
    "To maintain focus and simplify the analysis, such rare cases, which exceeded two solvents and three reagents per reaction entry, were excluded from the study.",
